OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate evening sunshine to end the day.
OL,7,FLargely clear skies overnight, though
OL,8,Flow cloud and mist potentially
OL,9,Freturning to eastern counties. A mild
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FAnother fine, dry and very
OL,13,Fwarm day. Any morning low cloud once
OL,14,Fagain quickly clearing to leave
OL,15,Fprolonged periods of strong sunshine
OL,16,Fthroughout Thursday. Calm winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
